4.1
.
Signiﬁcance
of
the
trends
This
study
relies
on
a
new
numerical
wave
hindcast
,
driven
by
wind
ﬁelds
originating
from
the
20CR
reanalysis
starting
in
1900
.
A
validation
of
wave
predictions
after
1955
was
undertaken
based
on
VOS
and
revealed
that
errors
for
yearly
—
mean
H5
were
of
the
order
of
5
%
.
A
